"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1932139-paris-olympics-tinder-dating-app\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  TheParis Olympicshas sparked a remarkable increase in Tinder activity in the city of love.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The competition hascaptivated global attentionand data from Tinder has shown how the Olympics has influenced the dating scene in the French capital.\", \"from\": 93, \"to\": 241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 153, \"end\": 159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tinder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0530316770068197e-18, \"text\": \"Tinder\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tinder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tinder\"}, {\"begin\": 226, \"end\": 232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9938692513661569, \"rank\": 0.005545563129495247, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the Olympic Village can ignite relationships, there are other avenues for the more than 10,000 Olympians to forge new connections.\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 253, \"end\": 268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999840838, \"rank\": 1.2486444093613932e-11, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before the official start of the Olympics, dating app Tinder experienced a 20 per cent surge in swipe activity across France, compared to last July.\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 498, \"end\": 504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9950691609597224, \"rank\": 0.003972836329815662, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There will always be people on the quest for love and other potential reasons for a sudden spike in Tinder's popularity.\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 630, \"end\": 636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tinder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0530316770068197e-18, \"text\": \"Tinder\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tinder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tinder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, a closer look at the data reveals a distinct Olympic theme, with a flood of fans from around the world also heading to Paris tosupport their country's leading stars.\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999934991592, \"rank\": 6.500790428704226e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From 1 to 25 July, the number of Tinder users listing Olympian as their profession rose by 52 per cent, while there was a 43 per cent increase in people listed as athletes on the app.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 883, \"end\": 891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999998059734214, \"rank\": 1.6293801978759272e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic stars would also have had the opportunity to scout out potential partners on Tinder before flying out to the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tinder's Passport Mode, which allows users to switch their location to Paris and message locals, saw a staggering 103 per cent increase in activity around key tourist areas in Paris during July.\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999934991592, \"rank\": 6.500790428704226e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1320, \"end\": 1325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999934991592, \"rank\": 6.500790428704226e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The USA, Brazil and Turkey ranked as the top three countries where people changed their location to France during the same period in July.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1343, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999998284001924, \"rank\": 1.7016116372903397e-07, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1348, \"end\": 1354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.99999706925789, \"rank\": 1.2480511354841141e-06, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 1359, \"end\": 1365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9999846916023989, \"rank\": 1.2904865794980877e-05, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}, {\"begin\": 1439, \"end\": 1445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9950691609597224, \"rank\": 0.003972836329815662, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, the Olympics have sparked a surge of Tinder users expressing their passion for sports.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gymnastics is the fastest-growing sport on the app, with a 31 per cent increase in people listing it as an interest last month.\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1815, \"end\": 1820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999934991592, \"rank\": 6.500790428704226e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1896, \"end\": 1908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9999414760473121, \"rank\": 5.8527365269117427e-05, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Football, basketball and swimming are the top three most popular sports on the app, with basketball seeing a 14 per cent rise in interest.\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tinder is accustomed to a summer surge in usage as people travel to new destinations.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  The data reveals that Passport Mode is used an average of 145,000 times per day, while those in the 18-25 age group using the feature send and receive three times more messages than those not using it.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2654, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, for any Olympic star needing extra privacy, incognito mode allows users to swipe normally, but only those they have liked will see them in their recommendations.\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2965, \"end\": 2978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2670574628020295e-14, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3014, \"end\": 3027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2670574628020295e-14, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"